REGISTER

Authorizations:
bearer
Request Body schema: application/json
required
lastname
required
string
firstname
required
string
phone
required
string
sexe
required
string
Enum: "M" "F"
password
required
string
app_type
required
string
Enum: "LOCAPAY" "LOCAPAY_BUSINESS"

Responses

Production Server

https://locapay-8f958cc17518.herokuapp.com/auth/register
